pmnch-subtext: Murakaza neza kuri "Icyo Urubyiruko Rushaka" Dashboard! Iki gikoresho gikorana gitanga ishusho yerekana ibisubizo nubushishozi dukusanya kuva mu rubyiruko rufite imyaka 10-24 kwisi yose. Intego yibikorwa ni ikibazo gifunguye: "Gutezimbere imibereho yanjye, ndashaka ...". Urubyiruko ruturutse hirya no hino ku isi rwagiye rusubiza ibi, biduha ubumenyi bwihariye kubyo bakeneye, ibyiringiro, n'ibyifuzo byabo. Shakisha amakuru, umenye inkuru ziri inyuma yimibare, kandi wifatanye natwe mukwongerera amajwi urubyiruko miliyari 1.8 kwisi yose. Kugira ngo umenye byinshi kubyerekeye ubukangurambaga, sura http://www.1 point8.org.
